    "name": "50MPa 20mm Enviro 50% SCM 100SL Conc",
    "manufacturer": "Boral Limited",
    "description": "Boral's ENVIROCRETE® concrete is a lower carbon concrete product which complies with AS 1379. It contains supplementary cementitious materials to reduce the portland cement content. ENVIROCRETE® concrete is available with two levels of portland cement reduction. ENVIROCRETE® 30% has a minimum portland cement reduction of 30% compared to the GBCA and ISC reference case and ENVIROCRETE® 40% has a minimum portland cement reduction of 40% when compared to the GBCA and ISC reference case. ENVIROCRETE® 30% and 40% are ideal for general applications where high-performance concrete is not required.",
